    "description": "Rift Sweepers is a 1-4 player co-op third-person shooter. As a Rift Sweeper, you will travel between dimensions and clear missions to protect the universe from collapsing. You will encounter strange and wacky enemies in odd and exciting challenges ahead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-4 PLAYER CO-OP</h2>Figure out how best to clear each mission alone or as a team. When playing as a team, identifying how to distribute roles for each mission and collaborating will make a huge difference.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 UNIQUE CHARACTERS</h2><br>Each character has unique weapons and abilities. The rifleman can move quickly and perform consecutive attacks. The sharpshooter can deal heavy damage. The demolisher is able to use a minigun to create explosions around him. The engineer can install turrets and give powerful buffs to his team.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MISSIONS</h2><br>As you travel through different dimensions, you'll encounter various missions that are strange and odd. These missions can be cleared alone while teaming up with friends will enhance your experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLES</h2><br>You'll encounter numerous enemies in whacky shapes and proportions. Evade enemies' attacks and find their weak points to destroy them.<br><br>DISCORD: ",
